:電影製作時，導演[[麥可吉|麥可吉]]認為貝爾是「世界上最可靠的動作明星」。<ref name=ignfirstlook>{{cite web|author=Orlando Parfitt|title=Terminator Salvation First Look|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/931/931531p1.html|date=2008-11-19|accessdate=2008-11-19|archive-date=2009-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207172553/http://movies.ign.com/articles/931/931531p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 麥可吉想要讓貝爾飾演馬可仕的角色，但演員－基於不知何故的理由－更想演出康納一角，使得角色的性格在編寫劇本過程不斷擴張。<ref>{{cite news|author=Meredith Woerner|title=John Connor Was Originally A Terminator 4 Supporting Character|work=[[io9|io9]]|date=2009-05-11|url=http://io9.com/5248232/john-connor-was-originally-a-terminator-4-supporting-character|accessdate=2009-05-11|archive-date=2009-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090514055853/http://io9.com/5248232/john-connor-was-originally-a-terminator-4-supporting-character|dead-url=no}}</ref> 貝爾是第一位確定名單的演員，已於2007年11月簽下合同。麥可吉至[[英國|英國]]與貝爾概略對談關於康納角色，當時正在拍攝《[[黑暗騎士|黑暗騎士]]》，而雙方也同意此拍攝計畫。<ref name=uk>{{cite news|author=Eric Goldman|title=Terminator Director Gives Hints|url=http://movies.ign.comarticles/861/861048p1.html|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2008-03-20|accessdate=2008-05-11}}{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref> 貝爾雖然是《[[魔鬼終結者|魔鬼終結者]]》系列的影迷，但起初他不感興趣，直到麥可吉說服他故事將會著重在角色人性描述，而非單單只是絢麗特效。<ref name=ignfirstlook/> 他們與沃辛頓持續地參予故事的討論。拍攝期間，麥可吉提到終結者道具壓到貝爾手部骨折。<ref name=brokenhand>{{cite news|author=Sophie Albers|title=Härter, lauter, Christian Bale|work=Rubriken stern.de|language=de|date=2008-11-22|url=http://www.stern.de/unterhaltung/film/:Terminator%3A-Die-Erl%F6sung-H%E4rter%2C-Christian-Bale/646550.html|accessdate=2008-11-25|archive-date=2008-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205125909/http://www.stern.de/unterhaltung/film/:Terminator%3A-Die-Erl%F6sung-H%E4rter%2C-Christian-Bale/646550.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 貝爾每天花六到八小時，與麥可吉在剪輯室給予建議至完成影片。<ref name=csny>{{cite news|author=Edward Douglas|title=Terminator: Salvation Roadshow Rolls Into NY!|work=ComingSoon.net|date=2009-01-13|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=51676|accessdate=2009-01-14|archive-date=2009-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090119053959/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=51676|dead-url=no}}</ref>
 
