ctMusic.com|date=2008-02-02|accessdate=2008-08-21|archive-date=2008-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080423080709/http://www.contactmusic.com/news.nsf/article/mcg%20wants%20day-lewis%20for%20terminator_1058225|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=brolin>{{cite news|author=A.C. Ferrante|title=Exclusive News: McG talks Terminator Salvation and hints at Josh Brolin to play a new foe|url=http://www.ifmagazine.com/new.asp?article=5690|publisher=iF Magazine|date=2008-02-06|accessdate=2008-02-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080207164353/http://www.ifmagazine.com/new.asp?article=5690|archivedate=2008-02-07}}</ref> 布洛林與貝爾談過，且看了劇本的草案，他發現「一些有趣和黑暗面，不過說到底，我不認為它適合我」。<ref>{{cite news|author=Josh Horowitz|title=Josh Brolin Confirms He Almost Signed On For ‘Terminator Salvation’|work=[[MTV|MTV]] Movies Blog|date=2008-11-25|url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2008/11/25/josh-brolin-confirms-he-almost-signed-on-for-terminator-salvation/|accessdate=2008-11-25|archive-date=2010-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100106130620/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2008/11/25/josh-brolin-confirms-he-almost-signed-on-for-terminator-salvation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

