[[美國電影協會|美國電影協會]]將本片評定為PG-13級，基於劇烈暴力科幻和動作場面，以及對白，不如以往的R級電影。<ref>{{cite news|title=Fox To Air Terminator Salvation “Extended Look”, Promo Confirms PG-13 Rating|work=/Film|date=2009-04-13|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/2009/04/13/fox-to-air-terminator-salvation-extended-look-promo-confirms-pg-13-rating/|accessdate=2009-04-14|archive-date=2009-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090415142428/http://www.slashfilm.com/2009/04/13/fox-to-air-terminator-salvation-extended-look-promo-confirms-pg-13-rating/|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 在同意刪去馬可仕用螺絲刀刺傷對手的一場戲後，協會才准許電影作下PG-13級的決定，麥可吉認為若只因為這場戲，而使得年輕的觀眾無法看到這部片是不公平的。他還刪除了[[蒙恩·布魯格|蒙恩·布魯格]]的裸露畫面，提到「這是一場男女之間毫無遮掩的一場戲，就像[[凱莉·麥吉莉絲|凱莉·麥吉莉絲]]與[[哈里遜·福特|哈里遜·福特]]在《[[證人|證人]]》一樣。但在最後，這場戲卻感覺有種不求回報的性慾，我不想在這故事與人物間周旋。」<ref>{{cite news|author=Ian Spelling|title=McG talks Terminator Salvation's ratings, deleted scenes, boobs and rants|work=[[Sci-Fi_Wire|Sci-Fi Wire]]|date=2009-05-09|url=http://scifiwire.com/2009/05/mcg-talks-terminator-salv.php|accessdate=2009-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090510063108/http://scifiwire.com/2009/05/mcg-talks-terminator-salv.php|archive-date=2009-05-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 
此評級也如製片所預期，現今電影評級標準對於PG-13暴力等級也越來越寬容，像是《[[終極警探4|終極警探4]]》。<ref name=friendly>{{cite news|author=Anne Thompson|title='Terminator' guns for kid-friendly rating|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2008-05-13|url=http://www.variety.com/VR1117985086.html|accessdate=2008-05-13|archive-date=2008-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080516073012/http://www.variety.com/VR1117985086.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

除了[[艾倫·丹·福斯特|艾倫·丹·福斯特]]著作的[[電影小說|電影小說]]外，將出版[[提摩西·桑|提摩西·桑]]所著的電影前傳小說「來自廢墟（From the Ashes）」。<ref>{{cite news|title=Terminator Salvation books on pre-order|work=Terminator Files|date=2008-08-23|url=http://www.terminatorfiles.com/news/2008/2008-08-23-a.htm|accessdate=2008-09-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080906201014/http://www.terminatorfiles.com/news/2008/2008-08-23-a.htm|archivedate=2008-09-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Titan's 'Terminator' Tomes|publisher=ICV2|date=2008-06-26|url=http://www.icv2.com/articles/news/12809.html|accessdate=2008-07-02|archive-date=2008-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080630222617/http://www.icv2.com/articles/news/12809.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 美國漫畫公司[[IDW|IDW]]亦發行四集改編電影的前傳漫畫。<ref>{{cite news|author=Matt Murphy|title=CCI: IDW's Ideals and Dreams|work=[[Comic_Book_Resources|Comic Book Resources]]|date=2008-07-26|url=http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=17450|accessdate=2008-07-28|archive-date=2008-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080828203541/http://www.comicbookresources.com/?page=article&id=17450|dead-url=no}}</ref> 講述2017年康納召集反抗軍的過程，收納仍存活的人類，化解彼此的偏執一同對抗天網。<ref>{{cite news|author=Jennifer Vineyard|title=EXCLUSIVE: Go Inside ‘Terminator Salvation’ With Our First Look At The Upcoming Prequel Comic!|work=[[MTV|MTV]] Movies Blog|date=2008-07-27|url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/07/27/exclusive-go-inside-terminator-salvation-with-our-first-look-at-the-upcoming-prequel-comic/|accessdate=2008-07-28|archive-date=2008-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080828170452/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/07/27/exclusive-go-inside-terminator-salvation-with-our-first-look-at-the-upcoming-prequel-comic/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 


